# vm-php-supabase-api-template

PHP Slim API for Supabase Auth. Not a Cloudflare Worker.

## Read order

`INSTRUCTIONS.md` → `index.md` → `.agents/skills/index.md`

## API contract

- `GET /health` — public
- `GET /me` — Bearer Supabase access token

Same JSON shape as `cf-hono-supabase-api-template`. Default local URL: `http://localhost:8080`.

## Code layout

- `app/src/` — routes, middleware, Supabase client
- `docker/` — Dockerfile + nginx
- `infrastructure/` — Terraform (Oracle) + cloud-init

## Deployment

See `docs/DEPLOYMENT.md`. Prefer Docker Compose; Terraform for Oracle Always Free.

## Pairing

Any auth-pack frontend; set `VITE_API_BASE_URL` and `ALLOWED_ORIGINS`.
